title: Renee Heartfelt - Death of the Ghost
description:
Renee Heartfelt, though containing former members of hardcore stalwarts Count Me Out, Striking Distance and Trial By Fire, sound nothing like their former bands. Instead, these boys from Richmond, VA have a sound similar to the rock stylings of Texas Is The Reason and Quicksand. (from last.fm)
